
<table width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td valign=top align=left width="40%">
      <h1>Welcome to Gear Goat! <%= image_tag("goat.jpg", size: "80x80") %></h1>      
    </td>
    <td valign=top align=left>
      <h3>Get Started!</h3>
        <table class=table width="100%">
          <tr>
            <td width="25%"><b><%= link_to "Inventory", gears_path %></b><br>How much gear do you really have? How much is it weighing you down? How old is it? Target new gear with wishlists.</td>
            <td width="25%"><b><%= link_to "Plan", packs_path %></b><br>Organize your gear in a Virtual Pack while you plan your trip. Streamline for optimal weight/utlity ratio.</td>
            <td width="25%"><b><%= link_to "Coordinate", "#" %></b><br>What's in your companion's Virtual Pack? Coordinate shared items and identify complementary gear.</td>
            <td width="25%"><b><%= link_to "Pack", "#" %></b><br>Finally, print a checklist of gear to ensure you pack everything. </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
